---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TrustedBy from '../components/TrustedBy.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Private Party Catering Vancouver | Birthday & Diwali Catering | Sula"
	description="Indian catering for birthdays, anniversaries, housewarmings, and Diwali parties in Vancouver. Live cooking stations, custom menus, full-service catering since 2010."
	canonical="/private-parties"
	ogImage="/uploads/private-party-vancouver-catering.webp"
>

	<Fragment slot="schema">
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
			"@context": "https://schema.org","@type": "Service",
			"name": "Private Party Catering Vancouver",
			"provider": {"@id": "https://sulacatering.com/#organization"},
			"areaServed": ["Vancouver", "Burnaby", "Richmond", "Surrey", "North Vancouver"],
			"serviceType": "Private Party Catering"
		})} />
	</Fragment>

	<section class="hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(74,21,84,0.7) 0%, rgba(184,149,106,0.2) 30%, rgba(37,4,45,0.85) 100%), url('/uploads/private-party-vancouver-catering.webp');">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1>Celebrations<br/>Worth <em>Remembering</em></h1>
			<p class="hero-tagline">From quiet anniversary dinners to multi-generational housewarmings, we cater the moments that matter most.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<TrustedBy />


	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro-block reveal">
				<h2>Catering for Life's <em>Best Moments</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
				<p>The big birthday. The first house. The fiftieth anniversary. Diwali with the whole family. <a href="/" class="body-link">Sula Catering</a> has been doing private party catering across Vancouver for fifteen years. Browse our <a href="/gallery" class="body-link">private party gallery</a>, add a <a href="/cafe-catering" class="body-link">live masala chai bar</a> from Sula Café, or read about <a href="/blog/halal-indian-catering-vancouver" class="body-link">halal catering for mixed gatherings</a>.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<img src="/uploads/birthday-catering-vancouver.webp" alt="Indian catering Vancouver birthdays parties" class="full-width-image" loading="lazy" />

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">Every Occasion</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">For Every <em>Celebration</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
			</div>
			<div class="service-grid-v2">
				<div class="service-card-v2 reveal">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/birthday-catering-vancouver.webp" alt="Birthday party catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Milestone Birthdays</span>
							<h3>Birthdays</h3>
							<p>From sweet sixteens to seventieth surprises, vibrant menus that capture the spirit of the celebration.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-100">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/indian-food-catering-near-me-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Anniversary dinner catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Marking Decades</span>
							<h3>Anniversaries</h3>
							<p>Plated dinner catering or buffet feasts, luxury menus that honour the moments that built a life together.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-200">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/indian-food-catering-near-me-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Housewarming catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">New Beginnings</span>
							<h3>Housewarmings</h3>
							<p>Welcome friends and family with abundant family-style Indian feasts, perfect for filling a new home with warmth.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-300">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/catering-services-vancouver-burnaby-richmond.webp" alt="Diwali catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Diwali, Eid & More</span>
							<h3>Holidays</h3>
							<p>Diwali, Eid, Christmas, Holi, full festive menus that bring family traditions to your table.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="image-banner image-banner-plum" style="background-image: url('/uploads/indian-food-catering-near-me-vancouver-bc.webp');">
		<div class="image-banner-content reveal">
			<h2>Live Stations.<br/><em>Lively Nights.</em></h2>
			<p>From chaat counters to dosa stations, turn dinner into theatre.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<section class="section section-plum pattern-mandala">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="experience">
				<div class="experience-img reveal-left">
					<img src="/uploads/private-party-vancouver-catering.webp" alt="Private party catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="experience-content reveal-right">
					<h2>Where Hospitality<br/>Meets <em>Heritage</em></h2>
					<p>A great party isn't just about the food, it's about the warmth around the table. We bring fifteen years of catering Vancouver's finest celebrations and pour it into every event we touch.</p>
					<p>From a quiet anniversary dinner for twelve to a multi-generational housewarming for two hundred, we scale up or down without compromising on the things that matter. Cocktail party catering, appetizer catering, finger food catering, or a full sit-down dinner with butter chicken, lamb biryani, and house-made naan. Add <a href="/corporate" class="body-link">corporate-style buffets</a> for office holiday parties too.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container-narrow">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">From Idea to Celebration</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">How It <em>Works</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
			</div>
			<div class="numbered-list">
				<div class="numbered-item reveal"><div class="numbered-num">01</div><div class="numbered-content"><h3>Tell Us <em>Your Story</em></h3><p>What's the occasion? Who's coming? What feeling do you want guests to walk away with?</p></div></div>
				<div class="numbered-item reveal"><div class="numbered-num">02</div><div class="numbered-content"><h3>Build Your <em>Menu</em></h3><p>Our chefs craft a custom menu that fits your guest count, dietary needs, and budget.</p></div></div>
				<div class="numbered-item reveal"><div class="numbered-num">03</div><div class="numbered-content"><h3>We Handle <em>the Details</em></h3><p>Setup, service, cleanup. You greet your guests, we take care of everything else.</p></div></div>
				<div class="numbered-item reveal"><div class="numbered-num">04</div><div class="numbered-content"><h3>You <em>Celebrate</em></h3><p>The party flows. The food flows. The guests linger because they don't want to leave.</p></div></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-dark pattern-damask">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="testimonial-block reveal">
				<p class="testimonial-quote">My mother's 70th birthday. 80 guests. Three generations. Every dish was perfect, the live chaat counter was the hit of the night, and the team made me feel like a guest at my own party.</p>
				<p class="testimonial-author">  Vikram · 70th Birthday Celebration</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">More Catering Options</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Continue <em>Exploring</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
			</div>
			<div class="related-links">
				<a href="/cafe-catering" class="related-link reveal">
					<div class="related-link-img"><img src="/uploads/Indian-food-catering-private-party.webp" alt="" /></div>

					<p class="meta">Service · Café Catering</p>
					<h4>Add a <em>Chai or Coffee Bar</em></h4>
					<p>Bring Sula Café to your party, masala chai stations, specialty coffee, fresh-baked Indian pastries.</p>
				</a>
				<a href="/weddings" class="related-link reveal delay-100">
					<div class="related-link-img"><img src="/uploads/indian-wedding-catering.webp" alt="" /></div>
					<p class="meta">Service · Wedding Catering</p>
					<h4>Wedding <em>Catering</em></h4>
					<p>Sangeet, ceremony, reception. Custom menus, live cooking stations, full-service execution.</p>
				</a>
				<a href="/gallery" class="related-link reveal delay-200">
					<div class="related-link-img"><img src="/uploads/birthday-catering-vancouver.webp" alt="" /></div>

					<p class="meta">Gallery</p>
					<h4>Private Party <em>Gallery</em></h4>
					<p>Real Vancouver celebrations we've catered, birthdays, anniversaries, housewarmings.</p>
					<span class="arrow">View Gallery →</span>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>


</Layout>
